<!-- Node: "Half-Life Q&A with Valve" -->
<div class="body_box_header">Half-Life Q&A with Valve</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/2" title="View user profile.">G.A.R.D.</a> on Thursday, February 12, 2004 - 06:04</small><br /><br />
Every think you wont to know about HalfLife 2 (and more) is revealed in an interview with Gabe Newell from Valve over on <a href="http://www.halflife2.net/article_valvespeak_1.php">Halflife2.net</a>. <br />
<br />
<b>Questions like:</b> What is the <i>flying manatee-like thing</i>? What is the <i>manipulator weapon</i>? Is there a <i>co-operative mode</i>? Will Half-Life 2 support Hyper-Threaded CPU's? Will HL2 support alt-tabbing out of the game? In the game if you shot a rocket at the ground would the ground deform as a result of the explosion? Does Half-Life 2 support <i>dynamic shadows</i> like Doom 3? Will HL2 run natively on <i>Linux</i>? When will you start making Half-life 3?
