<!-- Node: "Halo PC code leaked" -->
<div class="body_box_header">Halo PC code leaked</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/2" title="View user profile.">G.A.R.D.</a> on Tuesday, February 10, 2004 - 04:56</small><br /><br />
Talk is rife on the net that an older version of the Halo PC code has been leaked on the internet. Rumour has it that all beta version’s are individually numbered to track down the “Leak”. So once again another major game is in the public domain (this is becoming a problem!). Bungie and Gearbox ask that people refrain from accessing or posting links to web sites that contain the old Halo beta version. The official Gearbox response can be read on the Gearbox forum!!!
