<!-- Node: "Gold Llama Nominees Announced" -->
<div class="body_box_header">Gold Llama Nominees Announced</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/2" title="View user profile.">G.A.R.D.</a> on Tuesday, February 10, 2004 - 04:56</small><br /><br />
Well it isn’t the Oscars, but the new Gold Llama Nominees for 2004 have been selected this year, for recognition in great game movies. There are 12 categories:<br />
<br />
<b>Best Picture,  Best Audio, Best Tech,  Best Editing / Direction, Best Frag Movie,  Best Non-frag / Trickjump Movie, Best Presentation,  Breakthrough Video, Best Quake Movie,  Best Unreal Movie,  Best Counter-Strike Movie and Best RTCW Movie</b><br />
<br />
All Nominees this year were picked out by the ESReality admins. The winners will be announced in a week. You can check out all the nominees at <a href="http://www.esreality.com/?a=longpost&id=613171&page=2">ESREALITY::COM</a>.
